Class Summary 
Class Description
App
Main class that use input arguments and other class's method to generate the flight path of drone.
AppUtils
This class contains app's helper function.
Buildings
it's the implementation of building class, a building is used to store data of a no-fly-zone building.
Deliveries
This class is used for deliveries table in database.
Drone
The implementation of drone class with its methods.
Flight
it's the implementation of flight class, flight is used to store information about move from a position to another position.
FlightPath
This class is used for flight path table in database.
HttpUtils
This class includes 2 helper functions that used to send http request and get response.
LongLat
The implementation of LongLat class with its methods.
Menus
This class is used to handle data about shops and their items.
Orders
The implementation of order class with its methods.
Parse
This class provides helper function that used to communicate with database, either get data from it or write data to it.
